      <title>在特朗普建议美国钢铁投资之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/nippon-steel-slumps-after-trump-says-firm-may-invest-in-us-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）与日本总理史密斯·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）之间的一次密切关注的峰会上，日本钢铁公司在四个月内最大程度地减少了，这对公司收购美国钢铁公司的计划的不确定性提高了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/nippon-steel-slumps-after-trump-says-firm-may-invest-in-us-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 01:08:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将释放的以色列人质与“大屠杀幸存者”进行了比较</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-compares-freed-israeli-hostages-to-holocaust-survivors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他对本周末释放的以色列人质的衰减状况感到不安，并暗示美国对加沙地带的战争持续了耐心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-compares-freed-israeli-hostages-to-holocaust-survivors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 23:27:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔退出民意调查显示，Noboa的第一轮胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/ecuador-exit-poll-shows-noboa-scraping-narrow-first-round-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据当地电视频道Teleamazonas的一项出口民意测验，厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺贝亚（Daniel Noboa）在周日大选中勉强赢得了第一轮胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/ecuador-exit-poll-shows-noboa-scraping-narrow-first-round-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 22:32:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚的石油说，电视吐口水后，内阁发生了变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/colombia-s-petro-loses-another-minister-after-cabinet-quarrel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗（Gustavo Petro）说，他在上周一次混乱的电视转播内阁会议之后，要求他的部长辞职，以眼泪和谴责结束，并且已经导致三名官员辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/colombia-s-petro-loses-another-minister-after-cabinet-quarrel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 21:59:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普建议在财政部的马斯克努力发现不规则性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-suggests-musk-found-irregularities-in-us-treasuries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统建议，埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的政府效率团队在检查美国财政部的数据时发现了违规行为，并暗示这可能导致美国无视一些付款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-suggests-musk-found-irregularities-in-us-treasuries</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 21:38:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Scholz未能在德国选举电视辩论中获得决定性的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/scholz-fails-to-land-decisive-blow-in-german-election-tv-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理奥拉夫·舒尔茨（Olaf Scholz）努力在两周内在德国的抢断选举之前的两次电视辩论中的第一场比赛中，他迫切需要对保守派领先者弗里德里希·梅尔兹（Friedrich Merz）迫切需要的决定性打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/scholz-fails-to-land-decisive-blow-in-german-election-tv-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 21:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普宣布计划对钢，铝进口的25％关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-plans-to-announce-25-steel-aluminum-tariffs-on-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他计划对钢铁和铝的所有进口征收25％的关税，扩大他的贸易萨尔沃斯，并威胁到美国一些顶级贸易伙伴的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-plans-to-announce-25-steel-aluminum-tariffs-on-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 21:33:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科索沃的总理赢得选举，选民针对腐败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/kosovo-s-premier-set-to-win-election-as-voters-target-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科索沃总理在议会选举中取得了胜利，因为选民支持他的承诺扎根腐败并迅速融合塞尔维亚人占多数地区，即使他的做法使西方盟友感到愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/kosovo-s-premier-set-to-win-election-as-voters-target-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 21:21:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普急于释放行政权力击中司法墙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-s-rush-to-unleash-executive-power-hits-a-judicial-wall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官正在将刹车采取措施，这是唐纳德·特朗普总统任职前三周最引人注目的举动，这放缓了针对移民，联邦工人，政府支出和变性美国人的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-s-rush-to-unleash-executive-power-hits-a-judicial-wall</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着厄瓜多尔的民意调查，帮派暴力是选民的首要问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/gang-violence-is-top-issue-for-voters-as-polls-open-in-ecuador</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔（Ecuador）37岁的领导人丹尼尔·诺贝亚（Daniel Noboa）在周日寻求连任，而失控的帮派暴力是选民的首要问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/gang-violence-is-top-issue-for-voters-as-polls-open-in-ecuador</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 12:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
